credit.credit-words: WHO IS ON THE LORD'S SIDE?
"Then Moses stood in the gate of the camp, and said, Who is on the Lord's side?..." (Exodus 32:26).
Those who have not moral courage to conscientiously take their position in the face of unbelievers,
"It is soon to be known who is on the Lord's side, who wil not be ashamed of Jesus.
and imitate the self-denying life of Christ, are ashamed of Him,
leave the fashions of the world,
and do not love His example."
